Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.08,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And we're closing in on the \Nlast section of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:06.65,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,A nightmarish 874 meter downhill!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:14.78,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And here he is, the man who made his name \Nin Sector 3, driving the bright red 86 GT!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.35,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Plunging down Hakone's mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.79,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,this young man is blessed by gravity \Nin a way that seems miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.92,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,A new breed of driver,\N imported from England...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.02,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata is making a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:31.71,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Let's go.
