Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.53,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Things are taking a turn \Nfor the complicated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.68,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The pair fighting over third have run at \Na steady pace, and the 2 has caught them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:45.85,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,It's now a showdown between \Nthe 9 car, the 5 car, and the 2 car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.98,Default,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotta be tough for Sakamoto-kun, \Nwho's sandwiched between the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:03:00.61,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,His attention will be split \Nin front and behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:06.91,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting the 2 car \Nto make it this far up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:12.58,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,If he slips past me, it'll be \Na real pain in the ass to repass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:20.51,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna need to change tactics and \Nmake sure Akaba doesn't get past me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:28.31,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Aiba, why are you \Npretending to be a pace car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.65,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too stupid to manage your tires,\N stay out of the damn race!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.35,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a major development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:20.03,Default,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The central computer has just \Nplaced an attention flag on the 86!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:24.99,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely unprecedented! I can't \Nremember a single time it's happened before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.95,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,In qualifying, sure, but not in a race!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.79,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,28)}Kogashiwa-san, \Nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:34.04,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,28)}It's hard to say. What I'm \Nlooking at defies imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:39.46,Default,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way his tires haven't lost some\N of their grip. It's a physical impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.79,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:19.75,Default,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You don't have to tell me. \NHe's already in my mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.32,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We should've had the same margin entering\N Sector 3 that we had on the first lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.97,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,So what the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.09,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,He caught up with us a lot faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:44.13,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If he can pass us before \Nwe enter the death zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:48.95,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,even with a slipstream, we won't be able \Nto catch him on the Kamaboko Straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.82,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to do this, but there's no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.91,Default,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi! Change of plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:58.50,Default,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll alter our lines and keep him\N hemmed in! Blocking formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.72,Default,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.01,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,He made his move before we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:19.56,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,The second he caught up, he went to\N overtake me without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.52,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. He's in between us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.76,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But keeping him pinned in \Nbetween two cars works out fine for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:29.20,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can escape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.41,Default,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Sandwich formation time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.76,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pen him in until \Nthe Kamaboko Straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.37,Default,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.80,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,After catching up to the \NYashi-Kita Gang, the flag went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:03.23,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Getting stuck between those two cars\N has gotta be rough for Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:18.38,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,The Lotus is stopping him from \Nadvancing further with some deft blocking,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:21.92,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,while the Alfa Romeo is\Npressuring him from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:31.01,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,If he leaves himself open at all, \Nthe Alfa's nose will clip him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:36.21,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Kanata? \NHow do you deal with this mousetrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.06,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him through on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:46.63,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is some fine blocking \Nby the 18, the Lotus Exige.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:50.40,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's no way out \Nof this without stressing my tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.82,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara-sensei told me:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.30,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,"However tight it looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:08:00.02,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,if there's enough room for three cars \Nto go side by side, you can get past."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.80,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quite on Fujiwara-sensei's level yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:11.72,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But it's three-and-a-half \Ncar-widths here, and that's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.64,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And to conserve my tires, \NI'll need to execute this in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.36,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone? The 86 vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.03,Default,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! On your outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.48,Default,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.93,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's like his car warped to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.98,Italics,Nozomi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.09,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't right. I'm in a Lotus, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:13.28,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be the equal of all other \Nmanufacturers when it comes to cornering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.45,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a legacy that stretches all the way back \Nto when Colin Chapman was building them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:23.28,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It should trump a Toyota 86 \Nin every single department!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:28.25,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And he's through! The 86 is on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:33.46,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,He's in front of the Yashi-Kita Gang now,\Nand it happened in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:38.29,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,When they talk about "lightning fast," \Nthis must be what they mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:44.43,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,If you could see my arms right now, \Nyou'd be disgusted by all the goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.85,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise. What we just saw\N has genuinely shaken me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:54.81,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've imagined that the 86 \Nstill had enough grip in its tires to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:10:00.10,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd been torturing his tires\Nto compensate for his car's weaknesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:03.15,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,But it just goes to show \Nhow wide the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:10.29,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,This is the driving of the super elite\NKatagiri Kanata, from England's famous RDRS!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.99,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be no limit to what he can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.96,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,The announcer, Tanaka-san,\Nis talking about Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.64,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,About what you said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:26.17,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you've never \Ngone out with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.74,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be popular, \Ngiven how cute you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.72,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not popular at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:32.65,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.74,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I mean, boys {\i1}have {\i0}\Nconfessed to me before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:43.28,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I get cold feet. I just have \Nno confidence in my personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.24,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an only child,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:51.53,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,and since I was little, my parents have \Nalways said I'm selfish and self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:57.30,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about dating, I start worrying\Nthe other person might end up hating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:03.55,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? You seem \Nsweet enough to me, Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:10.73,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,And honestly, even if that is true, it's all \Nthe more reason to experience romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.69,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Love helps a girl grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.87,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be too selfish\N when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:23.26,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You have to consider how \Nthe other person feels, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:28.58,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,And if you care about the other person,\N you learn to do it naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:34.31,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Romance isn't just about fun. \NThere's plenty of hurt involved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:39.01,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't develop as a person \Nif you're afraid of getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:44.03,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,So if you wanna get on my level, \Nyou need to experience some quality romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.31,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that, you need to find the right guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.51,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,That was really encouraging!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:59.29,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I get in my head so much, \NI tend to overthink this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.61,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, there's someone \NI really like right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:07.14,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko-senpai, can I get relationship \Nadvice from you going forward, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.58,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:12.54,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial Black\fscx85\fs55\an1\blur0.3\c&H3F3A34&\t(\fscx105\fscy125)\move(116,230,64,242)}Katagiri Kanata
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.37,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.41,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we switch \Nto the battle for third.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.63,Default,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they've entered the ghost town \Ndeath zone, their pace has slowed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:33.06,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Even the punchy Akaba Kaito \Nhas calmed it down for this stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:39.15,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,It's an area of low visibility and few straights, \Nand these three cars are on the larger side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:42.91,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,It's fair to say there won't be \Nmany chances to pass for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:48.07,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,I'd put money on this stalemate \Ncontinuing into the back end of Sector 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.68,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And as the drone for the 86 \Nstruggles to keep up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:17.33,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,just now, it caught \Na glimpse of the car in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.32,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time since the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:27.43,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata has the 10 car's \NEmile Hänninen in his sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:38.36,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The rookie in his first race floors it\N as he aims to breach the top ten!
