Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.85,Top,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,MF Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:55.73,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The most difficult part of \NSector 3 is coming into view.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:07.28,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The red car disappears into the milky-white\N clouds. He is now in the death zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.74,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ogata-san, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.91,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Name it! Whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.46,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the course in this fog, clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.12,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.67,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see the other cars in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:27.59,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to call out the distance to the car \Nin front every time I'm a full second closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.23,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.76,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't really get why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.97,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you have the 10 in front \Nof you. He's 2.6 seconds up the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.20,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.74,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's two seconds flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.50,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you wanted? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.30,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly like that. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.89,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,One second exactly. Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:14.90,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.52,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.48,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.48,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.48,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.12,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.74,Italics,E.Han,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.58,Italics,E.Han,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman}Crazy boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.51,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata has dispatched Hänninen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:59.39,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked at the exact moment\Nthe 10's taillights became visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:03.68,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Using his lightning reflexes, \Nhe dived into the slightest of openings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.37,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see how you can \Nplan that kind of move.
