Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.11,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\shad0\bord1.2\fs12\c&H141416&\4c&H171718&\3c&HC2C6BB&\fax0.1\pos(306,238)\frz16.5\frx14\fry8}Age
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.11,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\shad0\bord1.2\fs12\an1\c&H141416&\4c&H171718&\3c&HC2C6BB&\frz16.5\fax0.1\pos(363,221)\frx14\fry8\frx14\fry8}years old
